---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="AI 競品分析 Dashboard — Case Study | AI PM INSIDER" description="AI 驅動的即時競品分析儀表板，支援自然語言查詢，將競品分析時間從 4 小時縮短至 30 分鐘。">

<!-- Hero / Header -->
<section class="relative bg-[#F9FAFB] pt-28 md:pt-36 pb-12 md:pb-16">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <!-- Back Link -->
    <a href="/#portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-body text-brand-subtle hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors mb-8 no-underline">
      <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-left-linear" class="text-lg"></iconify-icon>
      <span>返回作品集</span>
    </a>

    <!-- Tags -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-body rounded-full bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent-dark">Product Sense</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-body rounded-full bg-purple-600/10 text-purple-600">AI Dashboard</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Title -->
    <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-4">
      AI 競品分析 <span class="text-brand-accent">Dashboard</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Role -->
    <p class="font-body text-brand-subtle text-base md:text-lg">
      <span class="text-brand-text font-medium">Role:</span> Product Manager & Builder
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Overview -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[#F9FAFB]">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Overview</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">

      <!-- 問題 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:danger-triangle-bold" class="text-xl text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-text">問題</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          PM 做競品分析平均花半天，手動打開十幾個分頁，資料散落各處，且分析結果難以即時更新。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 目標 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:target-bold" class="text-xl text-brand-accent"></iconify-icon>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-text">目標</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          打造一個 AI 驅動的即時競品分析儀表板，支援自然語言查詢，讓 PM 用問的就能得到分析結果。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 成果 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:cup-star-bold" class="text-xl text-amber-400"></iconify-icon>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-text">成果</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          競品分析時間從 4 小時縮短至 30 分鐘，支援自然語言查詢，自動生成比較報告。
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Key Metrics -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6">

      <div class="text-center p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-amber-50 border border-amber-200">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-brand-accent mb-2">8x</div>
        <div class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">效率提升</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-amber-50 border border-amber-200">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-brand-warm-dark mb-2">30<span class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">min</span></div>
        <div class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">完成分析</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border border-emerald-100">
        <div class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-emerald-600 mb-2">即時</div>
        <div class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle">數據更新</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 產品架構圖 -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[#F9FAFB]">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Architecture</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-4xl text-brand-text mb-8 md:mb-10">
      產品<span class="text-brand-accent">架構圖</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Layer 4: Dashboard UI -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C5A55A 0%, #D4B86A 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;">Layer 4 — Presentation</div>
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Dashboard UI</div>
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-top: 4px;">Streamlit 視覺化呈現</div>
        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 10px solid transparent; border-right: 10px solid transparent; border-top: 10px solid #D4B86A;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 3: AI Engine -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #a78bfa 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;">Layer 3 — Intelligence</div>
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">AI Engine</div>
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-top: 4px;">Gemini AI 分析 + 摘要</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 10px solid transparent; border-right: 10px solid transparent; border-top: 10px solid #a78bfa;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 2: Data Pipeline -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #38bdf8 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;">Layer 2 — Processing</div>
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Data Pipeline</div>
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-top: 4px;">自動爬取 + 結構化</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 10px solid transparent; border-right: 10px solid transparent; border-top: 10px solid #38bdf8;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 1: Data Sources -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #64748b 0%, #94a3b8 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px;">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;">Layer 1 — Data Sources</div>
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px;">Data Sources</div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;">
          <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;">競品官網</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;">Product Hunt</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;">G2 Reviews</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;">新聞</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 核心功能 -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Core Features</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-4xl text-brand-text mb-8 md:mb-10">
      核心<span class="text-brand-accent">功能</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">

      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 bg-brand-light-surface border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:chat-round-dots-bold" class="text-xl text-brand-accent"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">自然語言查詢</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed mb-3">
          輸入「比較 A 和 B 的定價策略」，即時生成結構化分析結果，不需要寫任何查詢語法。
        </p>
        <div class="font-body text-xs text-brand-accent bg-brand-accent/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 inline-block">
          "比較 A 和 B 的定價策略" → 即時生成分析
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 bg-brand-light-surface border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-purple-600/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:radar-2-bold" class="text-xl text-purple-600"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">自動競品追蹤</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed mb-3">
          設定追蹤名單，系統每日自動更新競品的功能變動、定價調整與市場動態。
        </p>
        <div class="font-body text-xs text-purple-600 bg-purple-600/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 inline-block">
          設定追蹤名單，每日自動更新變動
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 bg-brand-light-surface border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:document-text-bold" class="text-xl text-amber-500"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">智慧比較報告</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed mb-3">
          一鍵生成多維度比較表格，涵蓋功能、定價、用戶評價、市場定位等面向。
        </p>
        <div class="font-body text-xs text-amber-600 bg-amber-500/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 inline-block">
          一鍵生成多維度比較表格
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 bg-brand-light-surface border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:bell-bing-bold" class="text-xl text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">趨勢警報</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed mb-3">
          當競品有重大功能更新、定價變動或融資消息時，自動推送通知，確保不錯過關鍵情報。
        </p>
        <div class="font-body text-xs text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 inline-block">
          競品有重大更新時自動通知
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 設計決策 -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[#F9FAFB]">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Design Decisions</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-4xl text-brand-text mb-8 md:mb-10">
      設計<span class="text-brand-accent">決策</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 max-w-3xl">

      <!-- Decision 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:code-square-bold" class="text-xl text-brand-accent"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">為什麼選 Streamlit？</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
              快速原型驗證是第一優先。Streamlit 讓我能在 Python 生態系中快速搭建互動式 Dashboard，不需要額外的前端框架。更重要的是，PM 團隊可以自己修改和擴展功能，降低對工程團隊的依賴。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Decision 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-purple-600/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:magic-stick-3-bold" class="text-xl text-purple-600"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">為什麼用 Gemini？</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
              競品分析需要處理大量長文本（產品頁面、評論、新聞），Gemini 的長上下文視窗（100K+ tokens）能一次處理完整資訊，避免分段處理造成的上下文遺失。此外，相比 GPT-4，成本更低，適合高頻自動化場景。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Decision 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:pen-new-square-bold" class="text-xl text-amber-500"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-2">Prompt Engineering 策略</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
              採用 <strong class="text-brand-text">Role + Dimensions + Format</strong> 框架確保輸出品質。先定義 AI 的角色（資深市場分析師），再指定分析維度（功能、定價、市場定位、用戶評價），最後規範輸出格式（結構化表格 + 關鍵洞察摘要），確保每次分析結果一致且可操作。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 技術棧 -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Tech Stack</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-4xl text-brand-text mb-8">
      技術<span class="text-brand-accent">棧</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-amber-50 text-blue-700 border border-amber-200">Python</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-700 border border-red-100">Streamlit</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 border border-purple-100">Gemini AI</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-green-50 text-green-700 border border-green-100">BeautifulSoup</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-body font-medium rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-100">Supabase</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- 反思與學習 -->
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[#F9FAFB]">
  <div class="site-container px-6">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-6">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent"></div>
      <span>Reflections</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl md:text-4xl text-brand-text mb-8 md:mb-10">
      反思與<span class="text-brand-accent">學習</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-3">PM 也能是 Builder</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          這個專案讓我深刻體會到，現代 PM 不需要等待工程資源。透過 No-code / Low-code 工具和 AI，PM 可以自己驗證想法、打造原型，甚至交付可用的產品。關鍵不是技術多強，而是能不能把問題定義清楚，然後找到最快的路徑去驗證。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-3">數據品質決定 AI 產品的天花板</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          開發過程中最大的挑戰不是 AI 模型，而是數據的結構化和清洗。網頁爬取的資料品質參差不齊，直接影響 AI 分析的準確度。最終花了約 40% 的時間在數據 pipeline 的優化上，這也是許多 AI 產品最容易被低估的環節。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-brand-light-border p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-brand-text mb-3">從使用者回饋中迭代</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-brand-subtle leading-relaxed">
          初版只有基本的查詢功能，但在內部測試後發現，PM 最需要的不是「查詢」而是「追蹤」——他們希望設定好競品名單後，每天自動收到變動報告。這個洞察讓我重新調整了產品的核心價值主張，從「AI 搜尋工具」轉向「AI 競品監控平台」。
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="site-container px-6 text-center">
    <p class="font-body text-brand-subtle text-sm mb-6">對這個專案有興趣？歡迎交流</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/#portfolio" class="mag-btn px-6 py-3 border border-brand-light-border text-brand-text font-heading font-medium rounded-full text-sm hover:border-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors no-underline">
        <span>查看更多作品</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/#contact" class="mag-btn px-6 py-3 gold-gradient text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-full text-sm no-underline">
        <span>與我聯繫</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
